1
00:01:41,560 --> 00:01:45,940
[Sword and Beloved]

2
00:01:59,470 --> 00:02:03,520
[Episode 2]

3
00:02:13,430 --> 00:02:14,040
Huaizhu,

4
00:02:14,870 --> 00:02:15,950
over these years,

5
00:02:16,870 --> 00:02:18,510
Fugui has lost all the joys

6
00:02:18,510 --> 00:02:20,000
a person should have,

7
00:02:21,750 --> 00:02:23,630
yet I can't go soft on him.

8
00:02:24,310 --> 00:02:25,000
I can't let down

9
00:02:25,000 --> 00:02:28,130
everything you've done for me
and for the Yiqi Alliance.

10
00:02:28,870 --> 00:02:29,590
A Soldier

11
00:02:30,560 --> 00:02:32,120
is born only to slay demons.

12
00:02:41,190 --> 00:02:41,800
Soldier,

13
00:02:42,000 --> 00:02:42,680
wait.

14
00:02:43,520 --> 00:02:44,240
It's me,

15
00:02:44,520 --> 00:02:46,850
the little spider who sent you the letter.

16
00:02:48,840 --> 00:02:49,900
This is horseweed.

17
00:02:50,360 --> 00:02:51,710
It has a great hemostatic effect.

18
00:02:51,710 --> 00:02:52,150
Here.

19
00:02:56,150 --> 00:02:56,800
No need.

20
00:02:58,000 --> 00:02:59,240
Your father was really mean

21
00:02:59,240 --> 00:03:00,400
to you.

22
00:03:00,560 --> 00:03:01,360
Plus,

23
00:03:01,520 --> 00:03:02,750
it's your birthday.

24
00:03:04,150 --> 00:03:05,120
I'm sorry, I'm sorry.

25
00:03:05,120 --> 00:03:06,310
I'm sorry. I was wrong.

26
00:03:06,310 --> 00:03:07,570
I didn't see anything.

27
00:03:07,960 --> 00:03:08,910
Take this.

28
00:03:09,190 --> 00:03:11,280
It contains pinellia, Dahurian angelica,

29
00:03:11,280 --> 00:03:13,080
dried beauveria, and cinnabar.

30
00:03:13,190 --> 00:03:14,520
If you simmer it for six hours,

31
00:03:14,520 --> 00:03:15,910
it's good for internal injuries too.

32
00:03:15,910 --> 00:03:16,800
And...

33
00:03:18,430 --> 00:03:18,800
Hey!

34
00:03:19,150 --> 00:03:20,560
I haven't finished yet.

35
00:03:21,240 --> 00:03:23,000
Why are you always like this?

36
00:03:35,560 --> 00:03:36,960
Your closest friends and loved ones

37
00:03:36,960 --> 00:03:38,910
dying one by one before your eyes—

38
00:03:39,310 --> 00:03:40,150
Do you know

39
00:03:40,150 --> 00:03:41,120
what it's like?

40
00:03:41,630 --> 00:03:43,760
The Hongye underneath the Jinlan Mask

41
00:03:44,000 --> 00:03:45,660
lost because of his emotions.

42
00:03:46,190 --> 00:03:48,000
He'll never forgive himself!

43
00:03:48,680 --> 00:03:51,310
I won't allow you to follow in
his footsteps!

44
00:03:57,630 --> 00:03:58,430
Father,

45
00:04:00,470 --> 00:04:02,280
what exactly are you hiding?

46
00:04:37,830 --> 00:04:38,680
This is...

47
00:04:39,270 --> 00:04:40,510
the Black Grief Tree?

48
00:04:42,600 --> 00:04:43,120
No.

49
00:04:43,720 --> 00:04:44,510
It can't be.

50
00:04:45,470 --> 00:04:47,190
I've already cut it down.

51
00:04:47,750 --> 00:04:48,720
This is fake.

52
00:04:48,720 --> 00:04:49,720
It's an illusion.

53
00:04:50,240 --> 00:04:51,390
Really?

54
00:04:54,720 --> 00:04:56,480
Wangquan Hongye,

55
00:04:56,480 --> 00:04:57,870
long time no see.

56
00:04:59,360 --> 00:05:01,070
Third Young Master of Aolai tried his best

57
00:05:01,070 --> 00:05:02,480
to draw a circle

58
00:05:02,480 --> 00:05:04,630
and protect you all,

59
00:05:05,430 --> 00:05:07,360
but you all arrogantly left the circle

60
00:05:07,360 --> 00:05:08,890
and got yourselves killed.

61
00:05:09,310 --> 00:05:10,630
All these years,

62
00:05:10,830 --> 00:05:12,750
you think you can change anything

63
00:05:12,750 --> 00:05:14,270
by raising a Soldier?

64
00:05:15,040 --> 00:05:17,630
Love is dying and hatred is rising
in the world.

65
00:05:17,630 --> 00:05:20,690
The Black Grief Tree will
eventually come back to life.

66
00:05:20,870 --> 00:05:21,870
And I

67
00:05:22,510 --> 00:05:24,000
am waiting to meet Wangquan Fugui,

68
00:05:24,000 --> 00:05:25,920
the blade you personally

69
00:05:26,160 --> 00:05:28,070
sharpened.

70
00:05:44,600 --> 00:05:45,510
It's a dream.

71
00:05:48,560 --> 00:05:49,560
But why is my dream

72
00:05:51,720 --> 00:05:53,850
always connected to the outer circle?

73
00:06:02,120 --> 00:06:03,000
Could it be...

74
00:06:12,270 --> 00:06:13,510
Wangquan Hongye,

75
00:06:14,190 --> 00:06:15,680
did you dream of me again?

76
00:06:16,680 --> 00:06:18,810
As long as there's hatred in the world,

77
00:06:19,160 --> 00:06:21,240
you won't be able to really kill me.

78
00:06:21,950 --> 00:06:23,430
Just wait

79
00:06:23,430 --> 00:06:25,240
to pay with your blood.

80
00:06:39,270 --> 00:06:40,560
Don't be shameless.

81
00:06:40,920 --> 00:06:43,380
The Soldier
celebrated his birthday alone?

82
00:06:43,600 --> 00:06:45,240
What kind of intelligence is this?

83
00:06:45,240 --> 00:06:46,680
Madam Yin is not patient.

84
00:06:46,950 --> 00:06:48,159
If she decides to
hold someone accountable,

85
00:06:48,159 --> 00:06:49,510
can we take the responsibility?

86
00:06:49,510 --> 00:06:50,390
If she did,

87
00:06:50,600 --> 00:06:51,800
she'd go to you first.

88
00:06:52,720 --> 00:06:54,050
Don't think I don't know

89
00:06:54,480 --> 00:06:55,610
you credit yourself

90
00:06:55,720 --> 00:06:56,830
for all my work.

91
00:06:57,750 --> 00:06:58,750
So what?

92
00:06:59,270 --> 00:07:01,600
Demons go by the law of
survival of the fittest.

93
00:07:01,600 --> 00:07:02,600
Crushing you

94
00:07:02,830 --> 00:07:04,600
is as easy as killing an ant.

95
00:07:04,720 --> 00:07:05,750
Don't forget

96
00:07:06,070 --> 00:07:07,390
that without me,

97
00:07:07,750 --> 00:07:08,880
you can't even enter

98
00:07:08,950 --> 00:07:10,750
the Soldier's home by yourself.

99
00:07:12,070 --> 00:07:12,560
You...

100
00:07:13,040 --> 00:07:14,440
How dare you threaten me?

101
00:07:14,480 --> 00:07:15,340
I know what to do

102
00:07:16,270 --> 00:07:17,330
about the Soldier.

103
00:07:18,360 --> 00:07:18,800
Hey!

104
00:07:22,480 --> 00:07:24,630
After I get the Soldier's intelligence,

105
00:07:24,630 --> 00:07:26,190
I'll kill you!

106
00:07:27,600 --> 00:07:28,310
Last night,

107
00:07:28,310 --> 00:07:30,240
I dreamed about the outside again.

108
00:07:30,830 --> 00:07:32,960
Ever since I returned from the outside

109
00:07:33,560 --> 00:07:36,040
my consciousness has been
connected to the outside.

110
00:07:36,040 --> 00:07:37,040
I can feel that...

111
00:07:37,560 --> 00:07:38,190
it

112
00:07:38,870 --> 00:07:39,750
is back.

113
00:07:42,920 --> 00:07:44,160
Recently, hostility has increased

114
00:07:44,160 --> 00:07:45,220
in the Demon Realm.

115
00:07:45,750 --> 00:07:48,430
More and more murderers
have crossed the border.

116
00:07:48,430 --> 00:07:49,360
I wonder

117
00:07:50,040 --> 00:07:51,840
if it's related to the Black Fox.

118
00:07:55,190 --> 00:07:55,800
So,

119
00:07:56,270 --> 00:07:59,470
Fugui must master
the Heaven-and-Earth Strike quickly.

120
00:08:00,310 --> 00:08:01,600
But Young Master Fugui

121
00:08:01,600 --> 00:08:03,270
is already doing his best.

122
00:08:07,630 --> 00:08:09,560
Let's not talk about this anymore.

123
00:08:10,120 --> 00:08:11,390
How's the Li family preparing

124
00:08:11,390 --> 00:08:12,990
for the Blue Sky Convention?

125
00:08:13,360 --> 00:08:14,690
The Blue Sky Convention

126
00:08:14,800 --> 00:08:16,860
is a grand event for the Yiqi Alliance

127
00:08:17,120 --> 00:08:19,430
to select young talents.

128
00:08:19,870 --> 00:08:22,240
This time,
the Peach Garden's Li family is hosting.

129
00:08:22,240 --> 00:08:24,190
Master Li is the most reliable.

130
00:08:24,630 --> 00:08:26,240
He has already sent out invitations

131
00:08:26,240 --> 00:08:27,800
and has made all preparations

132
00:08:27,800 --> 00:08:29,530
for the convention next month.

133
00:08:32,270 --> 00:08:34,190
Quzhuo probably didn't expect

134
00:08:34,920 --> 00:08:35,750
that one day,

135
00:08:35,920 --> 00:08:38,920
he'd become the most reliable master
of the Li family.

136
00:08:41,240 --> 00:08:42,870
His brother would be pleased

137
00:08:43,190 --> 00:08:44,360
if he knew in heaven.

138
00:08:45,429 --> 00:08:45,870
Yes.

139
00:08:47,150 --> 00:08:48,010
There's a guest

140
00:08:48,789 --> 00:08:50,320
not on the invitation list.

141
00:08:51,320 --> 00:08:51,750
Who?

142
00:08:53,909 --> 00:08:54,970
Fifteen years ago,

143
00:08:56,200 --> 00:08:58,630
he practiced witchcraft
with his demon core.

144
00:08:58,630 --> 00:08:59,720
After he was discovered,

145
00:08:59,720 --> 00:09:00,600
you

146
00:09:00,910 --> 00:09:02,640
took away his Wangquan surname

147
00:09:02,870 --> 00:09:05,000
and exiled him to the Western Regions.

148
00:09:05,200 --> 00:09:07,060
It's Quan Jingting, Master Quan.

149
00:09:10,600 --> 00:09:11,840
It's my cousin?

150
00:09:14,080 --> 00:09:17,030
I heard that he's very popular
among the people

151
00:09:17,390 --> 00:09:18,650
after subduing demons

152
00:09:19,550 --> 00:09:20,240
in the Western Regions

153
00:09:20,240 --> 00:09:21,440
and also gained fans?

154
00:09:22,670 --> 00:09:23,240
Yes.

155
00:09:24,000 --> 00:09:25,960
He brought your previously
favorite nephew, Young Master Rumu,

156
00:09:25,960 --> 00:09:26,910
with him.

157
00:09:28,000 --> 00:09:28,750
I heard

158
00:09:29,270 --> 00:09:30,930
they are on their way already.

159
00:09:54,600 --> 00:09:55,150
Great!

160
00:09:59,200 --> 00:09:59,960
Get out of the way!

161
00:09:59,960 --> 00:10:00,320
Move!

162
00:10:00,440 --> 00:10:00,970
Get lost!

163
00:10:01,270 --> 00:10:01,800
Get lost!

164
00:10:04,440 --> 00:10:05,240
I'm talking to you!

165
00:10:05,240 --> 00:10:05,480
Get lost!

166
00:10:05,480 --> 00:10:06,540
I'm talking to you!

167
00:10:07,120 --> 00:10:07,920
Go over there!

168
00:10:07,960 --> 00:10:08,360
You...

169
00:10:09,320 --> 00:10:09,720
You...

170
00:10:09,960 --> 00:10:10,510
Leave!

171
00:10:10,670 --> 00:10:11,240
Let's go.

172
00:10:24,270 --> 00:10:25,670
What are they carrying?

173
00:10:26,320 --> 00:10:27,630
It looks heavy.

174
00:10:28,550 --> 00:10:29,750
Who are these people?

175
00:10:30,030 --> 00:10:30,600
Shush.

176
00:10:31,030 --> 00:10:31,960
No matter who it is,

177
00:10:31,960 --> 00:10:34,030
they’re not someone we should mess with.

178
00:10:34,030 --> 00:10:35,120
Stop talking.

179
00:10:56,360 --> 00:11:01,080
[Quan Jingting,
Master of the Frontier Quan Family]

180
00:11:02,360 --> 00:11:04,080
Where is Wangquan Shouyi?

181
00:11:11,200 --> 00:11:13,530
Why would the elder of the Wangquan family

182
00:11:13,720 --> 00:11:14,630
be here

183
00:11:14,630 --> 00:11:16,480
in my small tobacco house?

184
00:11:18,750 --> 00:11:19,840
Stop pretending.

185
00:11:20,840 --> 00:11:22,840
Do you think I don't know

186
00:11:23,080 --> 00:11:25,440
who your true boss is

187
00:11:26,030 --> 00:11:28,560
and what this tobacco house
is truly selling?

188
00:11:30,790 --> 00:11:32,450
Extracting demon cores alive

189
00:11:32,790 --> 00:11:34,960
and developing forbidden medicine...

190
00:11:34,960 --> 00:11:38,220
You don't dare to sell it
under the Wangquan Manor's watch,

191
00:11:38,240 --> 00:11:40,870
so you're selling it
in the Western Regions.

192
00:11:43,910 --> 00:11:45,320
Do you need me to give

193
00:11:46,000 --> 00:11:48,150
the evidence to Wangquan Hongye?

194
00:11:59,240 --> 00:12:00,100
Are you afraid?

195
00:12:02,840 --> 00:12:05,360
Let me show you something else.

196
00:12:11,440 --> 00:12:12,240
Is that basalt?

197
00:12:12,240 --> 00:12:13,000
It looks so powerful.

198
00:12:13,000 --> 00:12:14,150
Whose swordsmanship is this?

199
00:12:14,150 --> 00:12:14,750
Could it be

200
00:12:14,750 --> 00:12:15,550
the Heaven-and-Earth Strike?

201
00:12:15,550 --> 00:12:16,030
This...

202
00:12:16,320 --> 00:12:16,960
This is...

203
00:12:21,510 --> 00:12:22,630
My son, Rumu,

204
00:12:24,510 --> 00:12:26,150
is an extraordinary genius.

205
00:12:28,510 --> 00:12:29,600
Two years ago,

206
00:12:30,080 --> 00:12:33,280
when he fought dragon demons alone
in the Western Regions

207
00:12:34,080 --> 00:12:35,940
and performed this sword move...

208
00:12:41,360 --> 00:12:44,360
It was already close to
the Heaven-and-Earth Strike.

209
00:12:54,480 --> 00:12:56,870
I was the legitimate heir of Wangquan.

210
00:13:00,550 --> 00:13:01,410
Many years ago,

211
00:13:03,120 --> 00:13:05,960
just because of a small mistake,

212
00:13:06,870 --> 00:13:10,440
Wangquan Hongye forced me
to change my surname to Quan

213
00:13:11,030 --> 00:13:13,240
and exiled me
to the Western Regions.

214
00:13:14,630 --> 00:13:17,320
The 15-year grudge
for having my surname taken—

215
00:13:19,550 --> 00:13:21,550
I’ve been waiting for this very day.

216
00:13:32,240 --> 00:13:33,480
Wangquan Shouyi!

217
00:13:35,550 --> 00:13:36,960
You coward!

218
00:13:37,600 --> 00:13:39,800
Do you only dare to hide in this brothel,

219
00:13:40,270 --> 00:13:41,360
smoking opium,

220
00:13:41,910 --> 00:13:44,480
and cursing Wangquan Hongye
behind his back?

221
00:13:48,510 --> 00:13:50,750
Elder Wangquan welcomes Master Quan.

222
00:14:05,200 --> 00:14:06,480
Wangquan Shouyi.

223
00:14:06,840 --> 00:14:08,550
Where are the people persecutred
by Wangquan Hongye

224
00:14:08,550 --> 00:14:10,870
that you promised me you'd gather?

225
00:14:15,630 --> 00:14:16,720
Technically,

226
00:14:17,510 --> 00:14:19,030
I'm your uncle.

227
00:14:19,030 --> 00:14:19,720
Right?

228
00:14:20,150 --> 00:14:22,150
You have no manners at all.

229
00:14:32,720 --> 00:14:33,750
My son Rumu

230
00:14:35,030 --> 00:14:37,670
will kill the Soldier
during the Blue Sky Convention

231
00:14:37,670 --> 00:14:39,330
and seize the Wangquan Sword.

232
00:14:39,360 --> 00:14:41,690
The Yiqi Alliance has many fence-riders.

233
00:14:41,910 --> 00:14:43,440
If my son takes the lead,

234
00:14:43,630 --> 00:14:44,670
you command everyone

235
00:14:44,670 --> 00:14:46,130
to follow me in revolting.

236
00:14:47,200 --> 00:14:48,240
The Yiqi Alliance

237
00:14:48,480 --> 00:14:50,440
will be in our hands.

238
00:14:56,000 --> 00:14:58,790
What a foolish and simple plan.

239
00:14:59,320 --> 00:15:02,030
I've always been simple
and straightforward.

240
00:15:03,720 --> 00:15:04,980
What about you, Uncle?

241
00:15:06,200 --> 00:15:08,840
If Wangquan Hongye found out
you developed evil medicine

242
00:15:08,840 --> 00:15:09,960
and sold them,

243
00:15:10,320 --> 00:15:11,520
have you ever thought

244
00:15:11,870 --> 00:15:13,270
what would happen to you?

245
00:15:14,840 --> 00:15:16,320
In the chess game of life,

246
00:15:16,600 --> 00:15:18,130
there are no perfect plans.

247
00:15:18,630 --> 00:15:20,750
Heroes are made by their times.

248
00:15:21,670 --> 00:15:23,030
If we work together

249
00:15:24,000 --> 00:15:25,440
and succeed,

250
00:15:26,360 --> 00:15:27,550
the Yiqi Alliance

251
00:15:29,440 --> 00:15:31,840
will be your cash cow.

252
00:15:37,360 --> 00:15:38,390
If you can also

253
00:15:38,910 --> 00:15:41,000
provide me a pill

254
00:15:41,000 --> 00:15:43,150
to improve martial power

255
00:15:43,720 --> 00:15:45,000
and my son takes it,

256
00:15:46,440 --> 00:15:48,910
the plan will be even more perfect.

257
00:15:51,870 --> 00:15:54,200
Even a vicious tiger doesn't eat its cubs.

258
00:15:55,030 --> 00:15:57,120
I don't want your

259
00:15:57,120 --> 00:15:58,580
tiny, disgusting things.

260
00:15:59,320 --> 00:16:01,320
I know you have better ones.

261
00:16:16,320 --> 00:16:16,910
Soldier.

262
00:16:17,670 --> 00:16:18,510
You're back?

263
00:16:19,150 --> 00:16:19,670
Here,

264
00:16:19,870 --> 00:16:20,360
a towel.

265
00:16:21,390 --> 00:16:23,990
I forgot to give you
a birthday gift yesterday.

266
00:16:25,080 --> 00:16:26,200
This chrysanthemum

267
00:16:26,200 --> 00:16:27,930
is for you, Young Master Fugui.

268
00:16:31,840 --> 00:16:33,170
Aren't you afraid of me?

269
00:16:33,200 --> 00:16:33,840
I'm not.

270
00:16:36,790 --> 00:16:37,600
Really?

271
00:16:38,000 --> 00:16:39,080
No need to scare me.

272
00:16:39,750 --> 00:16:40,270
I know

273
00:16:40,270 --> 00:16:42,330
you don't hurt the weak and innocent.

274
00:16:42,510 --> 00:16:43,910
If you wanted to kill me,

275
00:16:44,360 --> 00:16:46,120
you would have killed me

276
00:16:46,120 --> 00:16:47,550
when you first met me.

277
00:16:50,320 --> 00:16:51,240
Are you sure?

278
00:16:52,000 --> 00:16:52,840
Is it because

279
00:16:53,320 --> 00:16:55,480
you're a spy sent by the Silk Cave?

280
00:16:55,480 --> 00:16:56,140
Soldier...

281
00:16:56,960 --> 00:16:57,440
How...

282
00:16:57,440 --> 00:16:59,270
How did you find out?

283
00:16:59,870 --> 00:17:01,930
Madam Yin, Mistress of the Silk Cave,

284
00:17:02,080 --> 00:17:03,030
hates me so much.

285
00:17:03,480 --> 00:17:04,340
Over the years,

286
00:17:04,550 --> 00:17:06,510
she's trained countless spiders

287
00:17:06,510 --> 00:17:07,710
to spy on information

288
00:17:08,120 --> 00:17:09,910
and even sent demons to kill me.

