00:30:14,380 --> 00:30:19,290
♪ Be each other’s star
and meet at the end of destiny ♪

573
00:30:14,960 --> 00:30:16,090
Young Master Fugui,

574
00:30:16,310 --> 00:30:17,160
after I leave,

575
00:30:17,720 --> 00:30:19,050
when will you forget me?

576
00:30:20,480 --> 00:30:21,410
I almost forgot.

577
00:30:21,790 --> 00:30:23,200
You have eidetic memory

578
00:30:23,750 --> 00:30:25,550
You'll definitely remember me.

579
00:30:25,720 --> 00:30:26,790
I can no longer

580
00:30:26,790 --> 00:30:28,550
casually kill demons again.

581
00:30:30,440 --> 00:30:31,000
Do demons

582
00:30:32,440 --> 00:30:33,960
really all deserve to die?

583
00:30:45,030 --> 00:30:47,160
You even learned his sword technique?

584
00:30:47,510 --> 00:30:48,750
Not bad.

585
00:30:49,070 --> 00:30:50,920
I also learned
Soldier's diet, daily routine,

586
00:30:50,920 --> 00:30:51,960
and other habits.

587
00:30:53,030 --> 00:30:54,880
Does he have any weaknesses,

588
00:30:55,680 --> 00:30:56,510
such as

589
00:30:56,790 --> 00:30:57,880
emotionally

590
00:30:58,790 --> 00:30:59,960
or physically?

591
00:31:00,880 --> 00:31:02,160
No.12580 is slow.

592
00:31:02,480 --> 00:31:04,550
I couldn't find
any of his other weaknesses.

593
00:31:04,550 --> 00:31:05,640
Please punish me.

594
00:31:06,640 --> 00:31:08,160
Why would I punish you?

595
00:31:09,110 --> 00:31:11,350
You successfully got close to the Soldier

596
00:31:11,350 --> 00:31:13,400
and got such important information.

597
00:31:13,400 --> 00:31:15,030
I should reward you instead.

598
00:31:17,000 --> 00:31:17,680
Go ahead.

599
00:31:18,720 --> 00:31:20,550
Give this medicine to your brother.

600
00:31:20,550 --> 00:31:21,750
Thank you, Mistress.

601
00:31:21,750 --> 00:31:23,310
I shall take my leave.

602
00:31:27,590 --> 00:31:28,240
Mistress,

603
00:31:28,960 --> 00:31:30,480
even with the Soldier's sword technique,

604
00:31:30,480 --> 00:31:32,480
we still aren't his match.

605
00:31:34,310 --> 00:31:36,570
Of course this intelligence is useless.

606
00:31:36,960 --> 00:31:38,270
I didn't ask No.12580

607
00:31:38,270 --> 00:31:39,920
to sneak into Wangquan Manor

608
00:31:40,440 --> 00:31:42,880
for her to really gather intelligence.

609
00:31:44,200 --> 00:31:45,430
I want her

610
00:31:46,310 --> 00:31:48,240
to become the Soldier's weakness.

611
00:31:48,880 --> 00:31:49,480
Go.

612
00:31:49,960 --> 00:31:51,550
Investigate the Soldier's whereabouts.

613
00:31:51,550 --> 00:31:52,480
At the right time,

614
00:31:52,480 --> 00:31:55,550
arrange for the Soldier
to be reunited with his little spider.

615
00:31:55,550 --> 00:31:56,640
Yes, ma'am.

616
00:32:00,590 --> 00:32:02,480
Poor No.12580.

617
00:32:03,640 --> 00:32:05,440
She doesn't know anything yet.

618
00:32:17,880 --> 00:32:18,680
Young Master.

619
00:32:19,480 --> 00:32:20,740
There's a new mission.

620
00:32:20,960 --> 00:32:21,760
The Xin family

621
00:32:21,960 --> 00:32:23,880
was forced by the Raccoon Dog Demon King

622
00:32:23,880 --> 00:32:24,750
and had no choice

623
00:32:24,750 --> 00:32:26,750
but to retreat into a land of miasma.

624
00:32:26,960 --> 00:32:28,070
The Xin family's master

625
00:32:28,070 --> 00:32:29,870
asked the Yiqi Alliance for help

626
00:32:30,200 --> 00:32:32,350
to defeat this demon.

627
00:32:36,070 --> 00:32:38,400
The raccoon dog demon clan isn't violent.

628
00:32:39,160 --> 00:32:41,750
They've never crossed the border
since it was drawn.

629
00:32:41,750 --> 00:32:43,110
Why have they

630
00:32:44,000 --> 00:32:45,460
suddenly become radical?

631
00:32:46,590 --> 00:32:48,200
The old Raccoon Dog Demon King

632
00:32:48,200 --> 00:32:49,680
was kind and polite,

633
00:32:50,240 --> 00:32:51,240
but recently,

634
00:32:51,240 --> 00:32:52,960
the raccoon dog demon clan
had an internal conflict.

635
00:32:52,960 --> 00:32:55,020
A fierce raccoon dog demon named Fu Li

636
00:32:55,400 --> 00:32:56,680
killed the old king,

637
00:32:57,160 --> 00:33:00,000
and got a winged spirit pearl
that can absorb human spiritual power

638
00:33:00,000 --> 00:33:02,160
and help lower demons transform.

639
00:33:02,920 --> 00:33:04,050
They used this pearl

640
00:33:04,350 --> 00:33:06,480
to rampantly absorb the spiritual powers
of nearby human clans

641
00:33:06,480 --> 00:33:07,550
for their own use.

642
00:33:07,920 --> 00:33:09,550
The people suffered a lot.

643
00:33:10,000 --> 00:33:11,960
That's why they're asking
the Yiqi Alliance for help.

644
00:33:11,960 --> 00:33:12,680
Fu Li?

645
00:33:13,750 --> 00:33:14,750
I remember her.

646
00:33:15,550 --> 00:33:17,240
I read her information before.

647
00:33:17,240 --> 00:33:17,960
Young Master,

648
00:33:17,960 --> 00:33:19,090
you've worked hard.

649
00:33:21,790 --> 00:33:23,480
You like flowers?

650
00:33:24,000 --> 00:33:24,880
Then I will

651
00:33:24,880 --> 00:33:26,400
send more here.

652
00:33:30,400 --> 00:33:31,480
No need, Mr. Fei.

653
00:33:34,680 --> 00:33:35,410
In a few days,

654
00:33:36,270 --> 00:33:37,000
Yiqi Alliance

655
00:33:37,000 --> 00:33:38,920
will hold the Blue Sky Convention.

656
00:33:38,920 --> 00:33:39,750
Young Master,

657
00:33:39,750 --> 00:33:41,200
you must win.

658
00:33:41,510 --> 00:33:42,970
Then Master will allow you

659
00:33:43,960 --> 00:33:45,640
to go travel about.

660
00:33:46,830 --> 00:33:48,960
You won't have to keep looking at maps.

661
00:33:55,830 --> 00:33:57,430
In the future, I won't look at

662
00:33:58,110 --> 00:33:59,310
such useless things.

663
00:34:01,350 --> 00:34:02,150
I don't mean to

664
00:34:02,510 --> 00:34:04,310
reprimand you.

665
00:34:05,310 --> 00:34:06,680
You are lonely.

666
00:34:07,400 --> 00:34:09,070
The more one does,
the more mistakes one makes.

667
00:34:09,070 --> 00:34:09,750
Anyway,

668
00:34:10,640 --> 00:34:11,550
one thing.

669
00:34:13,030 --> 00:34:14,830
Don't blame the Master.

670
00:34:15,480 --> 00:34:16,680
If you want anything,

671
00:34:16,880 --> 00:34:18,240
just tell me.

672
00:34:21,630 --> 00:34:22,630
Okay, Mr. Fei.

673
00:34:28,960 --> 00:34:29,440
Sister,

674
00:34:29,800 --> 00:34:31,000
you did a great job,

675
00:34:31,440 --> 00:34:33,440
so Mistress specially rewarded us.

676
00:34:33,590 --> 00:34:34,150
Look.

677
00:34:34,360 --> 00:34:36,290
We have meat for dinner these days.

678
00:34:36,710 --> 00:34:37,920
You need to eat more.

679
00:34:38,280 --> 00:34:39,550
Look how skinny you are now.

680
00:34:39,550 --> 00:34:41,150
You're not as muscular as me.

681
00:34:41,630 --> 00:34:44,110
It's because I was injured
by the Yiqi Alliance.

682
00:34:44,110 --> 00:34:45,880
That's why I'm sickly and frail,

683
00:34:45,880 --> 00:34:47,150
always a burden to you.

684
00:34:47,150 --> 00:34:48,510
Actually, not everyone

685
00:34:49,550 --> 00:34:51,080
in the Yiqi Alliance is bad.

686
00:34:52,670 --> 00:34:53,800
You're so funny.

687
00:34:54,440 --> 00:34:56,040
How can there be good humans?

688
00:34:56,550 --> 00:34:57,760
Listen up.

689
00:34:58,110 --> 00:34:59,480
Mistress's next mission

690
00:34:59,480 --> 00:35:01,800
is to steal the winged spirit pearl
from the raccoon dog demon clan.

691
00:35:01,800 --> 00:35:03,190
Anyone that I call out

692
00:35:03,440 --> 00:35:04,699
must go on the mission.

693
00:35:05,590 --> 00:35:06,760
No. 11788.

694
00:35:07,440 --> 00:35:08,920
No. 12309.

695
00:35:09,360 --> 00:35:10,590
No.12581.

696
00:35:11,400 --> 00:35:13,320
You all will depart today.

697
00:35:15,480 --> 00:35:16,190
Sister,

698
00:35:17,000 --> 00:35:18,070
I'll get going.

699
00:35:18,070 --> 00:35:18,710
Wait!

700
00:35:20,070 --> 00:35:21,270
I'll go on his behalf.

701
00:35:51,230 --> 00:35:53,070
You mere spider demons,

702
00:35:53,070 --> 00:35:55,190
how dare you steal our magic weapon?

703
00:35:55,440 --> 00:35:57,150
Do you want to die?

704
00:35:57,150 --> 00:35:58,710
Am I going to die?

705
00:35:59,150 --> 00:36:00,280
Demon King Fu Li,

706
00:36:00,400 --> 00:36:01,930
come out to meet your death!

707
00:36:03,800 --> 00:36:04,480
This is...

708
00:36:05,320 --> 00:36:06,450
Young Master Fugui!

709
00:36:20,550 --> 00:36:23,810
I've long heard of the name of
the Yiqi Alliance's Soldier.

710
00:36:24,190 --> 00:36:26,250
I'll see what you're all about today!

711
00:36:41,000 --> 00:36:42,510
You're playing tricks.

712
00:36:45,400 --> 00:36:46,150
Come out!

713
00:37:04,670 --> 00:37:08,760
[Raccoon Dog Demon King, Fu Li]

714
00:37:07,400 --> 00:37:08,590
You are the Soldier?

715
00:37:09,230 --> 00:37:10,630
Not that impressive.

716
00:37:11,280 --> 00:37:13,230
Today, I'll use you as a sacrifice

717
00:37:13,400 --> 00:37:16,260
to celebrate me leading
the raccoon dog demon clan.

718
00:37:37,110 --> 00:37:39,150
The raccoon dog demon clan is the best
at transforming.

719
00:37:39,150 --> 00:37:41,080
Young Master, you must be careful.

720
00:38:21,190 --> 00:38:22,320
Soldier, die!

721
00:39:05,150 --> 00:39:05,950
Young Master.

722
00:39:06,070 --> 00:39:09,530
All the lower demons in Huangfeng Ridge
have been eliminated.

723
00:39:09,960 --> 00:39:10,630
Return.

724
00:39:28,670 --> 00:39:29,400
It's her.

725
00:39:30,880 --> 00:39:31,840
Why is she here?

726
00:39:42,230 --> 00:39:43,560
She's too badly injured

727
00:39:44,670 --> 00:39:46,030
to be saved.

728
00:39:47,480 --> 00:39:49,230
Young Master Fugui...

729
00:39:50,550 --> 00:39:51,680
Young Master Fugui.

730
00:39:52,030 --> 00:39:53,760
you probably never knew

731
00:39:54,230 --> 00:39:55,480
there are many

732
00:39:55,710 --> 00:39:57,800
insignificant beings like us
beneath your feet.

733
00:39:57,800 --> 00:39:59,530
Like this wild chrysanthemum,

734
00:39:59,840 --> 00:40:01,280
we also want to live.

735
00:40:01,440 --> 00:40:02,570
Young Master Fugui,

736
00:40:02,760 --> 00:40:03,550
thank you

737
00:40:03,960 --> 00:40:05,620
for giving me a chance to live.

738
00:40:06,880 --> 00:40:07,710
Unless...

739
00:40:17,400 --> 00:40:19,660
I can only revive her by refining my power

740
00:40:19,760 --> 00:40:21,490
with this winged spirit pearl.

741
00:40:24,510 --> 00:40:25,230
Perhaps...

742
00:40:26,760 --> 00:40:28,150
this is God's will.

